rter<br> <BR><img src=http://members.aol.com/dogfuchow/pie.jpg height=120 width=120></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Two short stories…</span><hr size=1> well, I've finished most of my site now, and I finally opened up the Excerpts section, so I have two short stories (I know, they aren't excerpts) ready to read. These are both more psychoanyalitic than they are action. That basically means there's descriptive violence, but the story doesn't revolve around it. It revolves more around that character's emotional detachment from society (or into society)<br>
<br>
Here's the main chooser if you wanna read both: <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://lordsmanor.freeservers.com/excerpts.html">lordsmanor.freeservers.com/excerpts.html</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
<br>
The first story is about a college student who suffers from a mental disorder (basically, he has bloodlust, and when he tastes blood, he goes into an uncontrollable rage while having violent hallucinations. I kinda slacked on this, so I decided I'd start on a novel (which will take me a lot of time and a ton of deadlines). It's called <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://lordsmanor.freeservers.com/excerpts/DCCShort.html"> Dreaming of Crimson Clouds</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
<br>
<br>
The second is about a freelance Yakuza sniper who will be killed no matter what whether he completes his mission (an assassination) or not. This concentrates on the sniper's philosophy and the Yakuza philosophy, and has a lot mroe research put into it than most of my others. It's called <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://lordsmanor.freeservers.com/excerpts/Yakuza.html">Sign of the Yakuza</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
<br>
Please critique. (And you can critique the site too, if ya want, although I swear I'm not suggesting that you do. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->     )<br>
 <p><b>Gaealord Gabriel Angelo Maokai III</b>
