<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> &quot;...before Sogeki could take advantage of Sogeki's position of power.&quot;<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
<br>
At the start of the last paragraph you use &quot;muffled boom&quot; as a description of the rifle report.  In my opinion this isn't an accurate description of the sound.<br>
<br>
My final point is a question of style.  I feel that the final sentence would be more powerful if you removed, &quot;it resembled.&quot; <br>
<br>
A good piece overall, which I enjoyed reading.  Aside from what I've detailed there were a few typos.  A little editing and it will fulfil it's potential. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#CCCCCC><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub25.ezboard.com/ulordgabriel3.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Lord Gabriel 3</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Karbonite</span><br> <font color=#336699>(2/25/02 8:17:48 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm26.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=523.topic&index=2>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> <BR><img src=http://members.aol.com/dogfuchow/pie.jpg height=120 width=120></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Two short stories…</span><hr size=1> Yeah, that sniper one isn't finished yet. I noticed a few problems (which you didn't mention) while I was updating, so I figured I'd leave em' for some critiques here. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :hat --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/pimp.gif ALT=":hat"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
